Cell.Text: You are? Very good.... may I see it?
Oh... what a terrible shame. Well, if you think you know where you left it and can retrieve it, you know where to find me.

Node.Caption: WIAddItem07No: Actually, I'm not sure I have it anymore.

Cell.Text: Excellent. Very good. This is exactly what I need to complete a series of studies I'm doing on Dwemer craftsmanship and magical resonance. | I simply must have this! I'll pay you double what it's worth.

Node.Caption: WIAddItem07Result: Sure, here take a look.

Cell.Text: [S] Wonderful. You've just made an important contribution to the advancement of a Dwemer scholarship.

Node.Caption: WIAddItem07HaggleSold: Sounds fair. Here you go. (Gain Gold)

Cell.Text: [S] Well... I suppose important research is worth every coin. Alright. You have yourself a deal. How's double and a half it's value in trade?
With this the world could have a better understanding of the Dwemer! | Come now, where's you're sense of propriety? Extorting an old man like this.

Node.Caption: WIAddItem07Persuade: I think you can do better than that. (Persuade)

Cell.Text: [S] Hold on there. I suppose, in the uh, interest of research, I, ah, can spare a few more coins. Double and a half it's value. That's all I can muster.
Hah! I"ll see to it the Jarl hears of you're abusing court scholars. Shame on you.

Node.Caption: WIAddItem07Intimidate: Not good enough. I'll shake the extra coin out of you if I must. (Intimidate)

Cell.Text: [S] Oh... well... I can see you have no appreciation for scholarship.

Node.Caption: WIAddItem07NoDeal: Not good enough. I'll hold onto this. You'll need to find another one.

Cell.Text: [S] I'm glad we could come to an agreement.
